txt.en: Orkish weapons can be found within the Harrowing of Morgul.\n\nYou should destroy any Orkish weapons that you find.
You have successfully destroyed the Orc weapons within Minas Morgul, and have done a great service to all those working to reclaim Minas Ithil from the remnants of Sauron's forces.
'The harrowing of Minas Morgul is upon us, [placeholder]. Perhaps the conflict within the city is just the opportunity to deal an additional blow to the Orcs. Will you assist us?'
There is much for the White Company to accomplish in reclaiming Minas Ithil from the remnants of Sauron's forces.
